strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">使英國有理由介入香港事務</span></ins></strong>, 這也是為什麼當初英國不給港人BC身份, 卻要弄出BNO, 而中國則要強加中國籍給香港人的根本原因 (英國不要收留港人; 中國收港人, 但條件是&rdquo;管得了&rdquo;的港人. 反正要抓人只要說句他是&rdquo;中國人&rdquo;就行) (結論1和3); b. 英國對香港的&rdquo;道義和責任&rdquo;乃建基在利益上, 尤其<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">正值英國脫歐, 香港將可成為英國經濟的救火員</span></ins></strong> (結論2)."},{"pid":"b601887f0779b53c8708e57988d11162a6f4b2ca","tid":1496002,"uid":119933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66fdbb0a6e45be2ac81339f7caa7beef5c08ced3","tid":1496002,"uid":119933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T10:03:21.000Z","msg":"希望大家支持和SHARE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/visa-waiver-program-vwp-should-be-given-british-national-overseas-passport-holder\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fvisa-waiver-program-vwp-should-be-given-british-national-overseas-passport-holder&d=eywEaFxHh3WcM61vPhP2LegMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=37f3c909\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/visa-waiver-program-vwp-should-be-given-british-national-overseas-passport-holder</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T00:08:06.000Z","msg":"推，可以收到email啦"},{"pid":"e0d93360cedcf624226d7cc485c44df6ceafc542","tid":1496002,"uid":288478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:31:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簽咗了"},{"pid":"e2eb11c5aa6f06ecaa316f75d383a9419aeab4df","tid":1496002,"uid":308875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T00:32:20.000Z","msg":"光復香港, 不要支籍<br />\n&ldquo;中國單方面宣稱中英聯合聲明已經失效，香港人該何去何從？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n用1分鐘嘅時間簽名，務求收集到10萬簽名將BNO平權議題推上議會討論<br />\n註: 轉BC後可傳俾97後<br />\